E PUTNAM PATRIOT PUBLISHED BY THE PATRIOT PRESS Incorporated KATHERINE C MACDONALDPresident THE year that will come to a close at midnight tomorrow will puzzle the future historians who undertake to analyze the motives and account for the unrest that has marked the pass ing of its twelve months Europe under a systematic Fascist policy of intrigue is waiting what destiny has in store for it In the Far East war in its most ruthless form is horrifying the civilized world The people of Spain are still in the agony of Civil War and the end is not yet in sight Here in our own country the year that started under such favorable conditions has undergone a business recession the causes of which are matter of controversy The President and his advisors while bidding for the cooperation of business in counteracting the letdown still show no inclination to modify the policies of drastic reform to which the administration is committed Congress it is true is showing some signs of having a mind of its own This is a favorable symptom that business and government may yet find neutral ground on which the countrys prosperity may forge ahead Here in New"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-06-28T01:09:39.594Z", "group": ["ndnp/ct", "connecticut-state-library-hartford-ct-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84022396/1937-12-30/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ct:batch_ct_collins_ver01:data:sn84022396:00517173903:1937123001:1137/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=442&w=329", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ct:batch_ct_collins_ver01:data:sn84022396:00517173903:1937123001:1137/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=884&w=658", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ct/batch_ct_collins_ver01/data/sn84022396/00517173903/1937123001/1137.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["putnam", "connecticut", "windham", "windh